devpkg

Usage
=====
-I  INSTALL
    Installs package from URL

    $ devpkg -I [URL]


-L  LIST
    List all packages that have been installed

    $ devpkg -L


-S  INIT
    Create the package database

    $ devpkg -S


-F  FETCH
    Download package from URL

    $ devpkg -F [URL]


-B  BUILD
    Build package from URL

    $ devpkg -B [URL]


Additional options
==================
-c  CONFIG OPTS
    Additional options to pass to ./configure

    $ devpkg -c "FOO=BAR" -I [URL]


-m  MAKE OPTS
    Additional options to pass to make

    $ devpkg -m "DEBUG=1" -I [URL]


-i  INSTALL OPTS
    Additional commands to pass to make

    $ devpkg -i "test install" -I [URL]

